name: A Phoenix set the stage
description:
They say we're 12 generations deep now, and you have about 2,000 or so great grandparents. Whether the stats add or not, it is evident, we keep coming back. 

Humanity still finds a way to survive and continue the flame.

And so from the ashes of the past, so the Phoenix sets the stage.

This is a special release since today marks the 1 year that this wallet has been collecting on the tezos chain. 

https://objkt.com/asset/tzcolors/322

So in its honor, I will release 322 editions.
